PAVED
Pt. 4/5 (Answers EP)

The chorus melody visited me in a dream after I had just woken up from the ache of unrequited love. The connection was etheric and like nothing I had felt before. Conversations were deep, passionate and soul-searching. Every bone in my body wanted to hold on as he began fading away. ‘Paved’ speaks to a broken promise disguised as a fated lesson in discernment.

Written & produced by ALYSS


♅

You said we could fly to the moon
Promised we would get there
Now we're stuck in memories
Caged by your complexity
But the both of us know
